title: Такое видео
overview: We live in a world of amazing and incredible phenomena that no one can explain. Secrets of nature, messengers from other worlds, mysterious animals and people with superpowers surround us in everyday life, and sometimes we don't even know about it. Our mission is to introduce you to them and teach you how to resist them. After all, there is only one way to protect yourself from them. It's laughter. Sincere and unstoppable.
